{"ID":"20250704165302-uanxtte","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20250704165302-uanxtte","title":"4匹配代价","type":"doc","updated":"20250704172949"},"Children":[{"ID":"20250704165302-75ulyin","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250704165302-75ulyin","updated":"20250704165409"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"匹配代价用来衡量像素之间的相似程度，代价越大，左右图相对应的像素点，越不相似"}]},{"ID":"20250704171750-groenaf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250704171750-groenaf","updated":"20250704171825"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"只能说各种匹配代价的表示方式和适用场景不同，按需选取"}]},{"ID":"20250704171828-q4a92cj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250704171828-q4a92cj","updated":"20250704171832"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"经典的如下"}]},{"ID":"20250704171832-6jdeewy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250704171832-6jdeewy","updated":"20250704171948"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"AD：变换放映像素点的灰度变化，在纹理丰富区域具有良好的匹配效果，基于单个像素点计算的匹配大家往往会受到图像噪声，光照不均等影响。相似度可靠性不高。"}]},{"ID":"20250704171959-994nisj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250704171959-994nisj","updated":"20250704172036"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"SAD：像素领域内对应位置的灰度差绝对值之和"}]},{"ID":"20250704172020-zul0qvx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250704172020-zul0qvx","updated":"20250704172100"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"SSD：像素的平方和，相对与SAD有更高的复杂度，因为具有乘法操作，SAD更加鲁棒。"}]},{"ID":"20250704172101-ob05iy1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250704172101-ob05iy1","updated":"20250704172210"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"NCC：归一化相关系数，归一化：消除对光照敏感的问题，对不同的嘎滚着强度更加鲁棒，复杂程度更高。NCC适合小窗口，SAD，SSD适合大窗口"}]},{"ID":"20250704172211-tpaschc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250704172211-tpaschc","updated":"20250704172949"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"census变换，选取集合区域的中心点，然后计算邻域内的像素与中心点灰度值的关系，大于等于则为1，小于为2，也称之为汉明编码：Hamming"}]},{"ID":"20250704172913-htz8yux","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20250704172913-htz8yux","updated":"20250704172913"}}]}